# Push notification credentials
# google-services.json and GoogleService-Info.plist are PUBLIC config files
# (Firebase docs explicitly say these are safe to commit). They contain
# package-name-restricted client IDs, not secret keys. Commit them so EAS
# Build can read them.
#
# fcm-service-account.json IS a real secret (private key). Never commit it —
# it's already uploaded to EAS credentials separately.
fcm-service-account.json
